    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>A frequently used building brick, composed of clays or shales (and sometimes other materials), which has been fired to hardness in a kiln.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
